OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,FStrains on recruitment within Jersey's
OL,7,Fcommunity service team could see more
OL,8,Fpeople given prison sentences,
OL,9,Faccording to the island's latest
OL,10,Freport on the Probation Service.
OL,12,FIt describes employing supervisors as
OL,13,Fan "area of ongoing concern", stating
OL,14,Fit has become "increasingly difficult
OL,15,Fto recruit community service staff due
OL,16,Fto the rates of pay, working hours,
OL,17,Fand the challenging clientele".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,FThe review goes on to explain that,
OL,7,Fwithout adequate staffing, "there is a
OL,8,Frisk that an ineffective service will
OL,9,Flead to increased numbers of offenders
OL,10,Fgoing into prison".
OL,12,FThis is because community service is
OL,13,Ffrequently offered instead of a
OL,14,Fcustodial term.
OL,16,FIt comes after the island's latest
OL,17,Fprison report showed a population
OL,18,Fincrease of 27% in the past two years,
OL,19,Fwith La Moye reaching 92% of its total
OL,20,Fcapacity in September 2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,FWhile the prison's limit sits at 200
OL,7,Finmates, the daily population last
OL,8,Fyear averaged 175.
OL,10,FMike Cutland, the island's Chief
OL,11,FProbation Officer, tells ITV News that
OL,12,Fthe staffing shortage has been
OL,13,Ftriggered by several retirements.
OL,15,F"We have to think of succession
OL,16,Fplanning", he explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,F"Historically, it's been a challenging
OL,7,Fjob to recruit to so we've got a
OL,8,Fpermanent advert out at the moment,
OL,9,Fand we're also working with Human
OL,10,FResources to review the terms and
OL,11,Fconditions."
OL,13,FWhilst Mr Cutland describes the job as
OL,14,F"very rewarding", he acknowledges the
OL,15,Fconsequences of failing to fill these
OL,16,Fpositions could be significant.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,F"Ultimately, the biggest concern would
OL,7,Fbe if we cannot staff a community
OL,8,Fservice team there would be delays in
OL,9,Forders starting, and that might affect
OL,10,Fthe confidence of the Courts", he says.
OL,12,F"What we mustn't forget is that
OL,13,Fcommunity service is a direct
OL,14,Falternative to custody - the prison is
OL,15,Falready quite full, and it's a far
OL,16,Fmore costly option than non-custodial
OL,17,Falternatives.
OL,19,F"So I think there are some strategic
OL,20,Fissues and challenges to overcome over
OL,21,Fthe next few months."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
