CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,FAnother challenge outlined in the
OL,7,FProbation Service's annual report is
OL,8,Fthe need to replace its electronic
OL,9,Fcase management system - the platform
OL,10,Fused to monitor and organise client
OL,11,Fcases.
OL,13,FIt was due to be replaced in March
OL,14,F2025, but the service's chosen
OL,15,Fsupplier withdrew from the contract at
OL,16,Fthe last minute.
OL,18,FHowever, Mr Cutland remains optimistic
OL,19,Fand is "hoping that we will have a new
OL,20,Fsystem in by the start of 2027".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,FOverall, he describes 2025 as an
OL,7,F"extremely successful" year, with the
OL,8,Fhighest completion rate of probation
OL,9,Fand community services in the last
OL,10,Ffive years.
OL,12,FSome of his team's key successes
OL,13,Finclude:
OL,15,F"I think that indicates a team that's
OL,16,Feffective, works well together, and
OL,17,Fgets good results", Mr Cutland says.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779214266
OL,3,CStaff shortages risk more people being
OL,4,Csent to prison
OL,6,F"Those completion rates are impressive
OL,7,Fif you look at comparators elsewhere,
OL,8,Fand I think it shows a motivated team
OL,9,Fthat supervises our clients
OL,10,Feffectively."
OL,12,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,13,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,14,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,15,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/8
